BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260524-us-depart@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260524
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260525
SUMMARY:Depart U.S. for Dublin
DESCRIPTION:Overnight transatlantic flight. Hydrate, sleep, and keep essentials in carry-ons.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260525-arrive-dub-fly-edi@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260525T070000
DTEND:20260525T211500
SUMMARY:Arrive Dublin; fly to Edinburgh; easy first night
LOCATION:Dublin Airport / Edinburgh
DESCRIPTION:Morning Dublin arrival, airport buffer, afternoon/evening DUB to EDI flight to verify, Edinburgh check-in, easy dinner and optional gentle walk. No rental car.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260526-edinburgh-classics@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260526T080000
DTEND:20260526T211500
SUMMARY:Edinburgh Castle, Camera Obscura, Chocolatarium, Calton Hill
LOCATION:Edinburgh
DESCRIPTION:Clustered Old Town/New Town day with Castle, Camera Obscura, Victoria Street, Chocolatarium, shopping/downtime, and sunset viewpoint.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260527-edi-belfast@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260527T073000
DTEND:20260527T213000
SUMMARY:Fly Edinburgh to Belfast; Titanic Belfast and Black Cab tour
LOCATION:Edinburgh Airport / Belfast
DESCRIPTION:Fly EDI to Belfast City preferred. Pick up rental car only after Scotland. Recommended: Titanic Belfast, rest, Cathedral Quarter street art and dinner. Black Cab is an optional swap, not an add-on.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260528-belfast-galway@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260528T080000
DTEND:20260528T210000
SUMMARY:Belfast to Galway/Salthill transfer
LOCATION:Belfast / Enniskillen or Athlone / Galway
DESCRIPTION:Long driving day over 3.5 hours. Strategic stretch/lunch stops, Salthill Prom, Galway dinner and Latin Quarter stroll.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260529-galway-cliffs-dromoland@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260529T080000
DTEND:20260529T210000
SUMMARY:Galway, Dunguaire, Burren, Cliffs of Moher, castle night
LOCATION:Galway / Cliffs of Moher / Dromoland Castle
DESCRIPTION:Scenic west-to-Clare day with Dunguaire photo stop, Burren, Cliffs of Moher, Dromoland Castle check-in and dinner.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260530-dromoland-killarney@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260530T083000
DTEND:20260530T210000
SUMMARY:Castle morning to Killarney National Park
LOCATION:Dromoland / Adare or Bunratty / Killarney
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy castle breakfast and grounds, drive to Killarney, check in, Ross Castle/Torc/Muckross sampler, Killarney dinner.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260531-dingle-peninsula@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260531T080000
DTEND:20260531T210000
SUMMARY:Dingle Peninsula day trip from Killarney
LOCATION:Killarney / Inch Beach / Dingle / Slea Head
DESCRIPTION:Long scenic driving day over 3.5 hours. Inch Beach, Dingle town lunch, Slea Head highlights, ice cream/harbor, return Killarney.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260601-killarney-cashel-kilkenny@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260601T080000
DTEND:20260601T210000
SUMMARY:Killarney to Kilkenny via Rock of Cashel
LOCATION:Killarney / Rock of Cashel / Kilkenny
DESCRIPTION:Long repositioning day over 3.5 hours. Rock of Cashel and Hore Abbey photo option, Kilkenny Medieval Mile and dinner.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260602-kilkenny-dublin-airport@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260602T080000
DTEND:20260602T210000
SUMMARY:Kilkenny to Dublin sampler and airport hotel
LOCATION:Kilkenny / Dublin / Dublin Airport
DESCRIPTION:Light Dublin city sampler, Grafton Street/sweets/shopping, airport hotel check-in, rental car return if practical, final packing.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260603-dub-depart@ireland-scotland-trip
DTSTAMP:20260510T000000Z
DTSTART:20260603T063000
DTEND:20260603T110000
SUMMARY:Dublin Airport departure at 11:00 AM
LOCATION:Dublin Airport
DESCRIPTION:Hotel breakfast/shuttle, arrive around 3 hours before U.S.-bound flight, check-in/security/preclearance, depart 11:00 AM.
END:VEVENT
